      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the median house price in Red Hill Brisbane?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Red Hill's median reflects strong demand for elevated inner-north properties with city views and character architecture. Pricing varies considerably depending on renovation quality, aspect and view lines, and block size. Properties on the upper streets with direct city outlooks consistently attract premium buyer interest. An appraisal gives you an accurate read on where your home sits relative to current sales.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell a home in Red Hill?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-presented Red Hill homes typically sell within 25 to 40 days. The suburb's combination of city proximity, elevated views and limited supply of genuine character homes draws a focused buyer pool. Properties priced correctly tend to attract competitive interest early in the campaign.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the lifestyle like in Red Hill Brisbane?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Red Hill has a quiet, residential feel unusual for a suburb less than 3 kilometres from the CBD. Tree-lined streets, predominantly owner-occupied homes and proximity to the Kelvin Grove Urban Village give it a genuine neighbourhood character. Residents walk to cafes, the QUT campus and the Queensland Conservatorium of Music, and enjoy uninterrupted city and ranges views from the upper streets on a clear day.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What types of homes are in Red Hill?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Red Hill is predominantly Queenslander and post-war character housing on sloping blocks. Many homes have been renovated to add contemporary living spaces while preserving original facades and high ceilings. There is also an active market for unrenovated properties: owner-occupier renovators compete consistently for homes with good bones and strong outlooks, which benefits sellers who present and price their properties well.</p>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

